#46.title: Add Latam Nodes validator
#46.message: This proposal adds Latam Nodes as a new validator to the network. At LatamNodes, we believe in the power of decentralization and the strength of the Latin American community. By offering validator services based right here in Latin America, we’re helping to ensure a more secure and diverse network infrastructure. Our mission is to empower local communities, boost blockchain adoption, and contribute to the region’s growth within the global crypto ecosystem.

#49.title: Replace the 0x0 Address with 0x805 in active_precompiles
#49.message: A bug in active_precompiles is causing failures in both the precompiles and the x/evm module due to incorrect parameter initialization. This proposal addresses the issue by substituting the 0x0 address with 0x805, ensuring stable and proper functionality for the precompiles and the x/evm module.
